assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但老婆因病冇做野<br />\n等住搵錢比兩個人食<br />\n仲要儲錢買樓<br />\n公屋居屋又冇得申請<br />\n好大壓力..我都想跳槽<br />\n但怕搵唔返呢份人工<br />\n真係進退兩難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>師兄，唔搵工唔知時運高啊。<br />\n<br />\n你唔行出第一步出去見工點知自己值咩價啊。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實我有諗過去見住工先</blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>見工個時會同新老細講埋你想要幾錢人工架MA<br />\n唔岩你咪唔要,再去見其他<br />\n點解咁都要諗?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n己經搵緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"825a563807946a3c06445f9dd688a1335b87ad4e","tid":556239,"uid":13268,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:21:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人工幾多？<br />\n再答你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n實際幾多就唔自爆喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n總之稅就有份交<br />\n居屋冇得抽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"802de594f6166e7f93984e20f638295ce1c0eaca","tid":556239,"uid":11962,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:25:40.000Z","msg":"女人根本唔適合做管理<br />\n利申：最憎女權"},{"pid":"c545102e779872235ea62e1c0e7ae6d29199ad75","tid":556239,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:27:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf5606632b3f10c109563811ae81bb4e4cf85d7a","tid":556239,"uid":76063,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:31:14.000Z","msg":"比我唔忍走人.. 如果你真係好似你咁講冇做錯過野<br />\nD野又係你跟你做.. 你走個老細仲驚過你<br />\n使乜比個只做management既人head住你"},{"pid":"8461563faf110198c3fc859d96e59df290fb7e61","tid":556239,"uid":16425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:33:02.000Z","msg":"走啦 仲幫佢奶真係傻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35a4b887625b7639b881a7c63386e20cd78ebdb5","tid":556239,"uid":45285,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:39:36.000Z","msg":"真心，試下搵工，日日返工都谷住谷住都身體都唔好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果真係本身做呢份工人工高，咁就做得HEA D，唔好將公司野咁上心~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW，就算點都好，最後都唔好開佢拖，我諗你都明開完拖，過兩日佢地都唔會有乜BAD FEELING，最多你會變成佢地茶餘飯後既笑話話題ONLY。<br />\n山水有相逄，走都要交足戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49d80d7631631b210313f4f9aca9167dadc961fa","tid":556239,"uid":4116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:42:21.000Z","msg":"70歲就死啦<br />\n激多兩下死快d<br />\n搏炒拎錢走<br />\n如果你嘅能力係出面生存唔到嘅<br />\n咁你就咪怨啦<br />\n一間公司三個怨婦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ff8f0f2128f04ad511badf5eb36ec7f116b71ef","tid":556239,"uid":34771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:44:21.000Z","msg":"黎個棒打白骨精<br />\n<br />\n包佢地以後無聲出"},{"pid":"7d0b0c34be790d20217ca96de0a1296d50127ac7","tid":556239,"uid":112747,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:47:31.000Z","msg":"因為你唔靚仔"},{"pid":"59239117e2cdfac6531b41ab96bc8da312dd00bf","tid":556239,"uid":13268,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:48:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>比我唔忍走人.. 如果你真係好似你咁講冇做錯過野<br />\nD野又係你跟你做.. 你走個老細仲驚過你<br />\n使乜比個只做management既人head住你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實呢個老闆曾經係好人<br />\n教左我好多野都比左好多機會我<br />\n我上手走左老闆差唔多冧檔時佢請左我返黎幫佢頂左5-6年<br />\n叫做有少少成績<br />\n點知無啦啦請左個另一個老屎忽上司返黎<br />\n話因爲佢冇工做所以幫佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n黎到就搞風搞雨，真係一朝天子一朝臣<br />\n依家工作繼續我做晒<br />\n有功就上司既，屎就我食晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n收左Bonus係時候搵下後路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ca0bcba7e14846e5ca72319c2d5b3a571f7f88ba","tid":556239,"uid":13268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心，試下搵工，日日返工都谷住谷住都身體都唔好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果真係本身做呢份工人工高，咁就做得HEA D，唔好將公司野咁上心~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW，就算點都好，最後都唔好開佢拖，我諗你都明開完拖，過兩日佢地都唔會有乜BAD FEELING，最多你會變成佢地茶餘飯後既笑話話題ONLY。<br />\n山水有相逄，走都要交足戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n谷住谷住..唉<br />\n間中仲要食安眠藥先訓到<br />\n依家唯有Hea住做，另外繼續搵工<br />\n唔會開佢拖，因為呢行好窄<br />\n第日有機會再見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6af66e37354d81eb6a772cdc1166c46af8892652","tid":556239,"uid":68742,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:53:04.000Z","msg":"其實點解做咗八年，會俾個新入嚟嘅人咁容易就破壞到你同老細之間嘅信任？<br />\n<br />\n其二係你做咗咁耐都揾人嚟 head 住你，唔係應該你做呢個位咩？<br />\n<br />\n咁問唔係話樓主你有問題，但係事出必有因，失咗信任好似大問題啲"},{"pid":"b43febea051ac99d5506b015c296dd6844670294","tid":556239,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:57:18.000Z","msg":"跳糟啦屌"},{"pid":"09ad55f967efee29bed931842f92180a816eb0eb","tid":556239,"uid":19725,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:57:51.000Z","msg":"如果你真係做得野 怕咩跳槽啊<br />\n搵定後門 同老細暗示會走 <br />\n佢知你真係做得野就自然留你 如果都唔留 你都可有可無啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cd090d07a549bf369bbcd97e1899c4ac877c43b1","tid":556239,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ca0bcba7e14846e5ca72319c2d5b3a571f7f88ba","tid":556239,"uid":13268,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-13T03:52:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心，試下搵工，日日返工都谷住谷住都身體都唔好。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果真係本身做呢份工人工高，咁就做得HEA D，唔好將公司野咁上心~<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBTW，就算點都好，最後都唔好開佢拖，我諗你都明開完拖，過兩日